quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  32,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim: fii …óee kaalfe yewtanooma ka fu…ó…óoode Simoore Albaqarah."
  32,2,"Jippagol ndee Alqur'aanaare nde Muhammadu (yo kisiyee) addi, ko jippiniraande e makko, immorde e Jey…óo winndere nden."
  32,3,"∆Åee heefer…ìe no wi'a: Muhammadu fefindi nde, o baki e Joomi maako. ∆äum wanaa non woniri! Si ko woni, ko nde goongaare nde sikke alaa e mu'un, jipporiinde ka Joomi maa…óa an Nulaa…óo, fii yo a jertin yim…ìe, …ìe Nulaa…óo araano e mun ado maa…óa, hul…ìinoroowo …ìe lepte Alla …óen. Belajo'o, …ìe feewiray e goonga kan, …ìe jokka, …ìe gollitira ka."
  32,4,"Ko Alla woni tagu…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, O tagi ko woni hakkunde majji kon e nder bal…óe jeegoo. Himo hattani tagugol …ói e nder dumunna …ìur…óo fotoowo ma majaango. Refti O toowi O fotondiri ka dow "Arsi", no haandiri e mawngu Makko. Alanaa on, onon …ìee yim…ìe, gaanin Alla, gi…óo heftoowo fii mon, maa tefanoowo on ka Joomi mon. E on waajitotaako, rewon Alla tagu…óo on, hara on rewidaali Mo e go…ó…óum goo?"
  32,5,"Alla no fewjana denndaangal fiyakuuji …óin ka kammuuli e ka leydi, refti …ói ∆¥eengira ka Makko, e nder √±alaande nde emmbere mun woni, duu…ìi ujunere e ko limoton onon yim…ìe …ìen aduna."
  32,6,"On fewjoowo fi …óum …óon fow, ko Anndu…óo ko wirnii e ko fee√±i, huunde suu…óaaki Mo e …óin …ói…ói, Foolu…óo yoftot e ay…ìe mun, Mo gooto foolataa, Hinnotoo jeyaa…ìe Makko gom…óim…ìe …ìen."
  32,7,"On labin…óo kala huunde nde O tagi. O fu…ó…ói tagudi Aadama ndin e loopal, no anndiranooka."
  32,8,"Refti O wa…ói genyol makko on …ìaawo makko, tagiraa…óo e ndihal sortondir-kal, kal o yalti e mun."
  32,9,"Refti O timminiri tagu ne…ó…óanke on fotndindirgol mo, O wutti e makko Ruuhu Makko on, e jurol Malaa'ikaajo halfinaa…óo …óum on. Refti O wa…óani on onon yim…ìe …ìen, nan…óe ko naniron, e gii…óe …óe yi'iron, e …ìer…óe …óe haqqiliron. Kono fan…óii ko yettoton …óin neemaaji Alla e dow moo…óon."
  32,10,"Sirkoo…ìe fennu…ìe ummital …ìen wi': E nee, si men maayii, fii amen mulii ka leydi, men wontii mbul-mbuldi, hara men wuurnitete kesun? Haqqil ja…ìaa …óum. Ko woni kam…ìe on, ko …ìe yeddu…ìe ummital, …ìe gom…óinaa …óum."
  32,11,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ìee sirkoo…ìe fennu…ìe ummital: Ko hunnata on wara on, ko Malaa'ikaajo maayde on wakkilaa…óo ∆¥eetitugol pittaali mon. refti ko ka Amen gaa tun, woni ruttorde mon √ëalnde Darngal, fii hasbeede yo…ìitee."